import { Flex, HStack, VStack,Text } from "@chakra-ui/layout"
export const Footer=()=>{
    return(
        <>
        <Flex width="full" bg="black" mt="165px" color="white" justifyContent="center">
            <HStack spacing={6} p={6}>
                <VStack>
                <Heading as="h3" size="lg">
                        (lg) In love with React & Next
                    </Heading>
                  <Text fontSize="lg">About us</Text>
                  <Text fontSize="lg">Contact us</Text>
                </VStack>

                <VStack>
                    
                </VStack>

                <VStack>
                    
                </VStack>
            </HStack>
        </Flex>

        </>
    )
}
